  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We wanted to see the parade, you know, as they were coming in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never thought-- we never felt it could do anything to us, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were out on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we see those tanks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- they were marching in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, I mean, we never [? thought ?] anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just-- we went outside to see them. coming in, that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was in-- in what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- in-- in '41 already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in-- in-- in '40, we-- we were winning the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when the Germans became allies with Italians-- so the-- the Italians came in and occupied certain part of Greece.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans came in and picked up [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] Athens, Salonika.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when it came to the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Cyclades, ?] which is the islands, the Italians occupied there, because they were allied.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they-- and then they kept it for a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They never bothered being, you know, who's Jewish or not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they-- they kept it cool, you know, for the few-- first few months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They kept it cool.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I believe it was [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] August, maybe July-August of '41, already they starting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They asked all the Jews from age 16 to 45 to-- to gather in-- to gather into [GREEK], which is the-- one of the famous-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how do you call [INAUDIBLE] in-- in English?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Like a big park, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they concentrate quite a few Jews down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody had to register their names-- you know, the people who went over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever went, you had to register their names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, I was young, so I didn't-- I was outside this.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
